{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "19", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "16", "M": "44", "S": "04"}}, "news": [{"title": "Ahmedabad: 20 houses, four shops demolished to widen road in Narol", "para": "Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation's estate department cleared land in Narol. Twenty residential houses and four shops were demolished. This action opened an 18-meter-wide road. Platforms and other encroachments were also removed. The corporation had issued prior notices to occupants. The demolition occurred in the presence of police after non-compliance.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/ahmedabad-demolishes-20-houses-and-4-shops-for-road-expansion-in-narol/129679834?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-203173/129679834.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Vadodara: Man cheats 16 of \u20b940 lakh in PMAY flat scam", "para": "Vadodara police have registered a cheating case against Harish Chauhan, who allegedly defrauded 16 individuals by promising PMAY flats.  Chauhan, posing as a VMC agent, collected approximately Rs 40 lakh from victims before disappearing.  One complainant reported paying Rs 6.83 lakh for a promised flat in Subhanpura. The accused is currently absconding.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/fraudster-dupes-16-victims-of-40-lakh-in-pmay-scam/129679777?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-57802/129679777.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "Karnataka eyes Japan partnership for smart city solutions in Bengaluru", "para": "Karnataka is set to collaborate with Japan on smart city initiatives in Bengaluru, aiming to leverage Japanese expertise for urban challenges. This partnership, facilitated by Japan's MLIT, will focus on areas like energy, wastewater, mobility, and disaster management, with the Greater Bengaluru Authority acting as the nodal agency.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/smart-city/karnataka-and-japan-forge-alliance-for-innovative-smart-city-solutions-in-bengaluru/129679751?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-81876/129679751.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "smart-city"}]}